# BuildKit reads this per-Dockerfile ignore (the image builds with the repo
# root as context, so keep the heavy + irrelevant trees out). examples/ and
# every packages/*/package.json stay in — pnpm --frozen-lockfile validates the
# lockfile against every declared workspace package.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
terraform
docs
sandbox-worker
**/*.test.ts
**/testdata
